Bashly - Bash CLI Generator

init
  Create the bashly source folder, and place a template configuration file in it

preview
  Generate the bash script to STDOUT

validate
  Scan the configuration file for errors

generate
  Generate the bash script and required files

add
  Add extra features and customization to your script

doc
  Show bashly reference documentation

completions
  Display the bash completions script or install it directly to your bash
  completions directory

render
  Render the bashly data structure using custom templates

shell
  Start an interactive shell where you can run bashly commands

Help: bashly COMMAND --help
Docs: https://bashly.dannyb.co
